source.name: Facilities Management--June 2011 Fire Panel Report, by Location, with Detail
source.description: A recap of the alerts that appeared on Cook County facility fire panels. A building's Fire Panel shows all alarm/alert activity for the building, The report also lists descriptions of each alarm.
